<https://www.chemotion-repository.net/pid/56408#step-5> a CHMO:0002582,
        prov:Activity ;
    dcterms:description "The crude product was purified via flash-chromatography (Interchim® puriFLASH XS520) on silica gel (PF-30SIHP-F0040) using cyclohexane/ethyl acetate 35:65 to 30:70 in 10 CV (1 CV = 52.7 mL; flowrate = 26.0 mL/min). The product 1-diphenylphosphoryl-2-fluorobenzene (2.33 g, 7.78 mmol, 86% yield) was obtained as a colorless solid." ;
